{"tid":1138680,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"轉工疑難 認真求意見","createTime":"2019-05-04T16:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T18:31:14.000Z","uid":252000,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"845c02ef124f0bf9d802477a81378ca1321cdb67","tid":1138680,"uid":252000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T16:37:34.000Z","msg":"FG 做緊份銀行工 但做左半年多啲想轉工<br />\n因為唔太鐘意個job nature<br />\n同埋覺得唔算多野學（又唔係話冇既）<br />\nP.S. contract to perm<br />\n<br />\n始終一開始返份新工實係有好多野學 尤其係FG<br />\n到後期就會有個period係冇咩新野學<br />\n除非轉左去另一team<br />\n（但係太fresh又唔會比你轉...）<br />\n<br />\n（另一方面其實都仲搵緊究竟自己適合咩工）<br />\n如果有機會試下其他自己有興趣既野 應唔應該去？<br />\n<br />\n考慮1: FG 未做夠一年就走 驚俾人覺得jumpy<br />\n考慮2: FG究竟應該學到野為先定同事上司關係為先 (我頂盡都係做多一年）"},{"pid":"ea4eb73eb63a5798272cd2d661d8260ce68871e7","tid":1138680,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T16:44:12.000Z","msg":"最大問題係你想做d咩先得㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n裝冷氣都學到嘢你去唔去做"},{"pid":"d179bb70e1bc6d58b29d98f0933cf4105bb3d423","tid":1138680,"uid":252000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea4eb73eb63a5798272cd2d661d8260ce68871e7","tid":1138680,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T16:44:12.000Z","msg":"最大問題係你想做d咩先得㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n裝冷氣都學到嘢你去唔去做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:00:30.000Z","msg":"想學啲要少少分析能力 寫到report既 甚至對下客<br />\n唔想普通做Ops咁 好易比人replace<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又冇咩晉升機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1901594a846c0c2a2dc62faf05c3fa0dd6c28ae6","tid":1138680,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d179bb70e1bc6d58b29d98f0933cf4105bb3d423","tid":1138680,"uid":252000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea4eb73eb63a5798272cd2d661d8260ce68871e7","tid":1138680,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim